title: Puppets from "Isle of Dogs" go on display in London
text:
Puppets from "Isle of Dogs" go on display in London Monday, March 26, 2018 - 01:25 
The models made for Wes Anderson's latest venture are on show at an exhibition in London which also features a ramen bar. Rough cut (no reporter narration) ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
